    "Then, the benefits, drawbacks, and development patterns of GANs were analysed.",
    "The authors specifically looked at the connection connecting GANs and parallelism logic, concluding that GANs holds lot of calliber for virtual-real interaction and integration in parallel systems research.",
    "Their experiment demonstrated that GANs provide significant algorithmic assistance for parallel intelligence.Lala et al. [16] compared contemporary Generative Adversarial Network architectures-in special, AdaGAN, VEEGAN, Wasserstein GAN, and Unrolled GAN-on data sources with various distributions, including synthetic and real datasets, and with regard to a number of widely accepted indicators for calculating mode collapse.",
    "According to the study's findings, Wassertstein GAN underperformed on the datasets, but AdaGAN consistently outperformed the other GANs on almost all of them.",
    "The test findings also revealed that since the measures did not produce reliable results, one metric was insufficient to quantify mode collapse for GANs.Yoo et al. [17] noted that a diverse family of GANs with improved performance in each generation was produced as a result of different sorts of GANs being investigated from various perspectives."
